would want to stay out of it too, so who would be the real belligerents of 
WW3? My guess is that on the Allied side we definitely have USA, Canada, 
Israel, UK and the EU as well as Ukraine and some Balkan countries 
including Croatia. On the Other side we will have Russia and Serbia, China, 
Syria and Iran.

which countries will decide to join the war. I think South Africa and 
Brazil will be on the Russian side seeing as they are part of BRICS. 
Australia might also join the war due to their close proximity to China.. 
it's really hard to tell at this point which countries will decide it is in 
their interest to join such a war and in some cases even which side they 
choose. Brazil India and South Africa remain wild cards, and I think they 
are the most significant of the lesser powers. (the superpowers being EU, 
USA, Russia and China). 
Either way it would be a bloody conflict and I don't think anyone is aiming 
at all out war. The only way WW3 is going to start is if someone does
